title: The Unband - Retarder (2000)
description:
This is Rock\&#039;n\&#039;Roll the way it was supposed to sound! Not that horrendous \"I-hope-the-girls-like-it\" crap like The Strokes. No! This is REAL rock! The kind that makes you envision crushed beer cans, sticky floors, cigarette smoke and drunk rowdy nights! You just don\&#039;t hear rock like this anymore! These guys sing about getting trashed, doing cocaine, swearing at the man...etc. All while providing simple rocking chords. Genius! Great music for a party, or if you want to go destroy something. If you\&#039;ve seen Super Troopers, then you\&#039;ve heard of the Unband. 

Rock Out!!!




14 tracks @ 320kbps
